Yeh ek chhoti si rukawat hai, lekin ghabrayein nahi! Yeh error isliye aaya hai kyunki Git aapki kuch files ko "rebase" (merge) karne ki koshish kar raha hai, lekin shayad wo files abhi aapke computer par kisi aur process ya program (jaise Chainlit ya VS Code) dwara "in use" (khuli hui) hain.

Ise fix karne ke liye ye steps follow karein:

1. Ek baar y dabakar dekhein
Jaise aapne y type kiya hai, agar process aage badh jata hai, to bahut accha. Agar woh baar-baar wahi error de raha hai, to ise forcefully band karein.

2. Agar woh atka hua hai (Abort)
Agar terminal freeze ho gaya hai ya baar-baar error de raha hai, toh ise cancel kar dein:

Ctrl + C dabayein (terminal mein).

Phir ye command type karein:
git rebase --abort
(Isse aap wapas normal state mein aa jayenge).

3. Asaan Tareeka: Git ko "Force" karna
Chunki aapka project abhi bilkul naya hai aur GitHub par sirf ek basic README file hogi, aap ye method try karein:

Sabse pehle, git add aur git commit kar lein (agar aapne abhi tak nahi kiya hai):

Bash
git add .
git commit -m "My code update"
Ab --force ke saath push karein:

Bash
git push -f origin main
(Note: -f ka matlab hai "Force". Ye GitHub ki purani files ko overwrite karke aapka local folder wahan upload kar dega).

Ek Zaroori Advice (Future ke liye)
Aap OneDrive ke folder (~/OneDrive/Desktop/veridoc_ai) mein kaam kar rahe hain.

Warning: Git aur OneDrive ka combination kabhi-kabhi problem karta hai, kyunki OneDrive files ko "sync" (cloud par upload) karne ki koshish karta rehta hai jabki Git bhi wahi files modify karta hai. Is wajah se "file access denied" ya "deletion failed" jaisi problems aati hain.

Meri Salah: Agar aage bhi aise errors aayein, to apne project folder ko OneDrive folder se bahar nikal kar kisi simple location par rakhein, jaise C:\Projects\veridoc_ai.

Abhi ke liye git push -f origin main chala kar dekhein, kya aapka code GitHub par dikhne laga?

ek kam karo sare command starting se do muje sab kuch firse karta hu me and github me jo readme file hai usko delete kar deta hu pehle abhi tab github me kuch aaya nahi hai

Yeh ek bahut achha decision hai! Saari cheezein fresh start karne se confusion nahi rahega.

Chaliye, pehle GitHub repo ko saaf karte hain, phir apne computer par sabse sahi tarike se setup karte hain.

Step 1: GitHub Repo saaf karein
Apne browser mein apni GitHub repository (veridoc_ai) kholein.

Agar wahan koi files (jaise README.md) dikh rahi hain, toh unhe delete karne ki zaroorat nahi hai.

Repository Settings mein jayein (Upar 'Settings' tab).

Niche scroll karein aur "Delete this repository" par click karke use delete kar dein.

Ab ek Bilkul Nayi Repository banayein usi naam se (veridoc_ai)—lekin is baar kisi bhi box (README, .gitignore, License) ko tick MAT karna. Isse aapki repo ekdum khali rahegi.

Step 2: Computer par naye siray se start karein
Apne terminal (Git Bash) mein us folder (~/OneDrive/Desktop/veridoc_ai) ke andar jayein aur ye commands run karein:

1. Purani git history delete karein (taaki naya setup ho sake):

Bash
rm -rf .git
2. Naya Git setup karein:

Bash
git init
3. Apni identity wapas set karein (taaki commit mein dikkat na aaye):

Bash
git config --global user.email "amanjp5711@gmail.com"
git config --global user.name "Aman"
4. Files ko add aur commit karein:

Bash
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit - Fresh start"
5. Branch ka naam 'main' karein:

Bash
git branch -M main
6. GitHub se link karein (Apna naya wala URL use karein):

Bash
git remote add origin https://github.com/Aman-p02/veridoc_ai.git
7. Upload (Push) karein:

Bash
git push -u origin main
