Bas niche diye gaye 7 steps ko apne terminal mein ek-ek karke run karein. Sabse pehle apne computer ke usi folder (veridoc_ai) mein Git Bash open kar lein:

Step-by-Step Commands:
Bash
# 1. Purani history hata dein (agar pehle kuch error aaya ho toh)
rm -rf .git

