git commit -m "Remove .env and add .gitignore"
GitHub par bhej dein:

Bash
git push -u origin main
Agar is baar bhi "Secret violation" wala error aaye:
Toh iska matlab hai ki Git ko abhi bhi purani history mein wo key mil rahi hai. Is case mein aapko Force Push karna padega jo purani history ko override kar dega:

Bash
git push -u origin main --force
Kuch aasaan baatein yaad rakhein:

.gitignore ka file name: Make sure ki file ka naam sirf .gitignore hai (VS Code mein rename kar ke check kar lein).

API Keys: GitHub server ne aapki key detect kar li thi, isliye security ke liye wahi key Google Cloud Console par jaakar delete (revoke) kar dein aur nayi key generate kar lein.

