amanj@ASUS_X515 MINGW64 ~/OneDrive/Desktop/veridoc_ai (main)

$

Aap abhi bhi wahi error dekh rahe hain kyunki Git reset --hard HEAD~1 karne ke baad bhi us purani "commit" (jisme secret tha) ko puri tarah se nahi hata raha hai, aur GitHub abhi bhi us purani commit ko dekh raha hai.

Isse fix karne ka ek hi sahi tareeka hai: History ko overwrite karna.

Chaliye, bina commit ki history ke ek naya start lete hain. Ye steps dhyan se follow karein:

1. Repository ko pura "reset" karein
Ye command aapke local folder ko GitHub se completely alag (detach) kar degi aur aapka current state ek dam "fresh" ho jayega:

Bash
rm -rf .git
git init
2. .gitignore ko confirm karein
Abhi apne folder mein check karein ki .gitignore naam ki file wahan maujood hai ya nahi. Uske andar .env likha hona chahiye.  
TXT

3. Files ko phir se Add aur Commit karein
Bash
git add .
git commit -m "Fresh start without secrets"
4. GitHub remote phir se link karein
Bash
git remote add origin https://github.com/Aman-p02/veridoc_ai.git
5. Force Push (Sabse zaroori step)
Kyunki humne history naye sire se banayi hai, hamein GitHub ko batana hoga ki purani sab history bhool jao aur naya code accept karo:

Bash
git push -u origin main --force
Ek important baat:
Agar iske baad bhi error aaye, toh iska matlab hai ki aapke local folder mein abhi bhi .env file padi hai jise Git detect kar raha hai.

Push karne se pehle ye check zaroor kar lein:

Apne folder se .env file ko temporary kisi dusri jagah move kar dein (Desktop se bahar rakh dein).

Ab git add . aur git commit karein.

Ab git push -u origin main --force karein.

API Key warning: GitHub server par aapki key pehle hi "block" ho chuki hai. Jab aapka code successful push ho jaye, toh Google Cloud Console par jakar us specific API Key ko Delete kar dena, kyunki wo ab insecure maani jayegi.

Try karein, is baar error nahi aayega!




Gemini is AI and can make mistakes.

